jql.description:
A valid JQL query. Must include an ORDER BY clause. Do NOT use linkedIssues() — use issue in childIssuesOf("KEY") for parent/child relationships.

@example "assignee = currentUser() AND status != Done ORDER BY updated DESC"
@example "issuetype = Bug AND priority = High ORDER BY created DESC"
@example "issue in childIssuesOf(\"PROJ-123\") AND issuetype = Story ORDER BY created DESC"

additionalFields.description:
Optional list of extra Jira field names to include in each result. Use human-readable names — the tool resolves them to the correct field IDs automatically.

@example ["labels", "sprint"]
@example ["fix version", "components"]
